&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;2X FULL TIME POSTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;1X PART TIME POST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A vacancy has arisen within the Resources, Equipment and Decontamination Services (REDS) Team. This role supports the procurement, storage and transport of resources and equipment within the operating theatres and clinical environment. You will be expected to work on an individual basis, but also as an integral member of the REDS team within the Critical Care, Theatres, Anaesthetics, Pain and Sleep (ITAPS) Clinical Management Group and work accordingly to the department&#39;s policies and procedures, up-holding Trust policy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will also be expected to maintain a high standard of proficiency against the department&#39;s Quality performance requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will be required to participate in evening and weekend working across sites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;PREVIOUS CANDIDATES NEED NOT REAPPLY.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date: 22-November-2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Victoria Brayshaw- Williams, Service Manager-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
